  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1 \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0ba3\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0b9a\u0bbf \u0b95\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u00a0 - \u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8, \u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bc7 \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Two demonstrations dispersed by tear gas shelling - action near Fort, Parliament Circle",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The demonstration of the farmers who wanted to go towards the presidential palace in the fort and the demonstrations led by the Union of the Protection of Mineral Resources who wanted to go towards the Parliament were dispersed by using many methods.",
        "While two cases have been filed in the High Court regarding the crisis faced by the farmers, the case came up for consideration today.",
        "After the case, a group of farmers and supporters of the farmers wing of United People's Shakti, led by MPs Nalin Bandara and Dushara Indunil, marched to the fort via Kurakottai from Puduk Kada High Court premises.",
        "They tried to advance towards the President's House through Chetham Road. The police and action forces stopped the demonstrators who went ahead by violating the first road block of Chetham Road at the second road block. While the riot police were called there, the demonstrators were dispersed by water cannon and teargas attack. It is worth noting that about three times tear gas was fired at the demonstrators from time to time.",
        "Meanwhile today the Kaniya Resources Defense Union has taken up the protest action. It is noteworthy that the protestors were teargassed near the entrance road of the Parliament."
      ],
